# ── Agent session debris (never commit these) ──────────────────
*.log
session_progress.json

# ── Autonomous agent tracking files (ephemeral — gitignored by design) ──────
# These are regenerated by the initializer at the start of every run.
# They MUST NOT be committed — a prior-run "all pass" state on origin/main
# caused an agent to shortcut all work by syncing remote state (RC-9).
# The local file is the only authority during a run.
feature_list.json
claude-progress.txt
autonomous_build_log.md
*-run.log
*.backup.*
*.bak
init-session*.log
session2*.log
autonomous-implementation-run.log
issues.log
compliance-evidence.log
log_entry_*.txt
verify_*.sh
extract_*.py
parse_features.py
*_extraction*.json
*_progress*.json
sla-compliance-*.json
